      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "⚛️ FRONTEND\nReact 18 + Vite + Tailwind CSS v4\n─────────────────────────────\n📦 Libraries\n  • React Router v6 (routing)\n  • Tailwind CSS v4 (styling)\n  • Framer Motion (animations)\n  • React Hook Form (forms)\n  • Axios (HTTP requests)\n  • react-leaflet (GPS map)\n  • jsPDF + html2canvas (PDF)\n  • Lucide React (icons)\n  • Vite PWA Plugin (offline)\n\n🗂️ State Management\n  • AuthContext\n    JWT token + inspector info\n  • InspectionContext\n    Multi-step inspection state\n\n🔒 Auth Flow\n  • ProtectedRoute wrapper\n  • JWT stored in memory/cookie\n  • Auto-redirect on token expire\n\n☁️ Deployed on: Vercel",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 11,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "⚛️ FRONTEND\nReact 18 + Vite + Tailwind CSS v4\n─────────────────────────────\n📦 Libraries\n  • React Router v6 (routing)\n  • Tailwind CSS v4 (styling)\n  • Framer Motion (animations)\n  • React Hook Form (forms)\n  • Axios (HTTP requests)\n  • react-leaflet (GPS map)\n  • jsPDF + html2canvas (PDF)\n  • Lucide React (icons)\n  • Vite PWA Plugin (offline)\n\n🗂️ State Management\n  • AuthContext\n    JWT token + inspector info\n  • InspectionContext\n    Multi-step inspection state\n\n🔒 Auth Flow\n  • ProtectedRoute wrapper\n  • JWT stored in memory/cookie\n  • Auto-redirect on token expire\n\n☁️ Deployed on: Vercel",
      "lineHeight": 1.5
    },

