      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "⚙️ BACKEND API\nNode.js + Express + TypeScript\n─────────────────────────────\n🛣️ Routes\n  POST   /api/auth/register\n  POST   /api/auth/login\n  GET    /api/auth/me\n  POST   /api/inspections\n  GET    /api/inspections\n  GET    /api/inspections/:id\n  POST   /api/inspections/:id/field\n  POST   /api/inspections/:id/stages\n  PATCH  /api/.../stages/:stageId\n  POST   /api/reports\n  POST   /api/reports/:id/submit\n  POST   /api/upload/image\n\n🛡️ Middleware\n  • verifyToken (JWT guard)\n  • multer (file upload)\n  • errorHandler (global)\n  • zod (input validation)\n\n🔧 Core\n  • Drizzle ORM (SQL builder)\n  • bcryptjs (password hash)\n  • jsonwebtoken (JWT)\n  • Nodemailer (report email)\n\n☁️ Deployed on: Railway",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 11,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "⚙️ BACKEND API\nNode.js + Express + TypeScript\n─────────────────────────────\n🛣️ Routes\n  POST   /api/auth/register\n  POST   /api/auth/login\n  GET    /api/auth/me\n  POST   /api/inspections\n  GET    /api/inspections\n  GET    /api/inspections/:id\n  POST   /api/inspections/:id/field\n  POST   /api/inspections/:id/stages\n  PATCH  /api/.../stages/:stageId\n  POST   /api/reports\n  POST   /api/reports/:id/submit\n  POST   /api/upload/image\n\n🛡️ Middleware\n  • verifyToken (JWT guard)\n  • multer (file upload)\n  • errorHandler (global)\n  • zod (input validation)\n\n🔧 Core\n  • Drizzle ORM (SQL builder)\n  • bcryptjs (password hash)\n  • jsonwebtoken (JWT)\n  • Nodemailer (report email)\n\n☁️ Deployed on: Railway",
      "lineHeight": 1.5
    },

